name: le
description: Output: less than or equal to (<=)

name: ge
description: Output: greater than or equal to (>=)

name: range
description: Output: range from start value to one less than end

name: all
description: Output: true if all elements evaluate to true

name: any
description: Output: true if any element evaluates to true

name: sorted
description: Output: returns sorted copy of list

name: reversed
description: Output: returns a reverse list iterator

name: ord
description: Output: Unicode value of inputted character

name: chr
description: Output: character at inputted Unicode value

name: read
description: Output: looks at the whole document as a string

name: readline
description: Output: looks at each line as a string

name: randint
description: Output: random integer between low and high

name: grid
description: Output: adds grid to next graph

name: zeros

name: ones
description: Output: list with number of rows, number of columns, and number of 1.0s

name: transpose
description: Output: the transpose of the array

name: max
description: Output: vector of maximum values of columns

name: min
description: Output: vector of minimum values of columns

name: std
description: Output: returns standard deviation of array

name: genfromtxt
description: Output: array with data from file
